{"tid":1768143,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟今日生日","createTime":"2019-12-04T01:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T15:19:11.000Z","uid":56537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1871b9596b5e826718cb5a166f2a4a1380d79ff6","tid":1768143,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"咁多年生日願望都係為自已去祈求<br />\n<br />\n讀好書搵到女朋友搵到好工 etc<br />\n<br />\n但呢五個月 轉變好多 有夢發除非有事都會參與<br />\n<br />\n星期六日拍拖節目都係發夢 又要返工 又要讀pt degree<br />\n<br />\n真係好累 有時好想話休息下 <br />\n<br />\n心入面就諗起上千手捉點比人打 點比人傷害 被捕<br />\n<br />\n好嬲 好想班黑驚 高官 中共 死晒。<br />\n<br />\n今年生日願望好簡單<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8979832defbdadd9421cd15a9b2906ec34e23df6","tid":1768143,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9153fd05f5e640bf950ff9fc7aa0fc3f7ab1c630","tid":1768143,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193735f1373b0365e977b739c1312ceeb0d5eb3e","tid":1768143,"uid":28944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"生日快樂立立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ef2c2fc371cab22320a91e9b2688d2e8917e5a","tid":1768143,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0098173a974ea68fb8549a5cf54cb11c9f1218","tid":1768143,"uid":171969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:16:17.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"35d1e27a261d095ccf3db145c08649a38d577563","tid":1768143,"u